comments: Schroder (TOR) has a resting hand as he trails Miller (CHA), and releases when Miller receives the pass.
Quickley (TOR) legally contests Martin's (CHA) jump shot attempt.
Quickley (TOR) steps toward Martin (CHA), and marginal contact occurs as he releases away during the drive.
Bridges (CHA) toward the basket when marginal body contact occurs after Poeltl's (TOR) release on his put-back shot attempt.
Bridges (CHA) reaches toward the ball and does not make contact with Barnes' (TOR) arm during Barnes' jump shot attempt.
Barnes' (TOR) shot attempt does not make contact with the rim, and a 24-second violation is correctly assessed.
Bridges (CHA) gives a step of distance when establishing himself in Quickley's (TOR) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Bridges (CHA) commits a take foul on Schroder (TOR).
Schroder (TOR) commits a take foul on Miller (CHA).

Replay review of the foul called on Barrett (TOR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Barrett (TOR) extends his right arm into Richards (CHA) as he's airborne and initiates illegal body contact that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Miller (CHA) reaches in and initiates illegal contact with Schroder's (TOR) arm in the backcourt, affecting his SQBR.
Quickley (TOR) legally contests Bridges' (CHA) jump shot attempt.
Barnes (TOR) legally contests Miller's (CHA) jump shot attempt.
